    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a dependable daily driver. The exterior does show its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, though it remains functional and comfortable. Mechanically, the car runs well, but you should expect the typical maintenance needs associated with a well-used vehicle. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
